  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On May 5, 2026 at 05:01 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>New Delhi: <a href=\"/tag/redcliffe+labs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Redcliffe Labs</a> has elevated <a href=\"/tag/gaurav+jain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gaurav Jain</a> to the role of <a href=\"/tag/chief+operating+officer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Chief Operating Officer</a> (COO). Jain will lead growth initiatives and oversee operations and clinical quality, reflecting the company’s focus on nurturing leaders from within as it scales its technology-driven <a href=\"/tag/preventive+diagnostics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">preventive diagnostics</a> platform across India.With over two decades of experience in <a href=\"/tag/pharmaceuticals+and+diagnostics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">pharmaceuticals and diagnostics</a>, Jain brings extensive expertise in business growth, operational excellence, and scalable execution across multiple verticals.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Jain joined the company in November 2021 as Senior Vice President and Head of Growth, where he initially led expansion initiatives and strategic growth opportunities. He later spearheaded the development of the company’s home-collection phlebotomy network, strengthening last-mile connectivity and service reach.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>Commenting on the appointment, Aditya Kandoi, Founder and CEO of <a href=\"/tag/redcliffe+labs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Redcliffe Labs</a>, said, “From driving growth initiatives to strengthening field operations, supply chain, and lab efficiency, <a href=\"/tag/gaurav+jain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gaurav Jain</a> has consistently taken ownership of critical business functions and delivered impact at scale.”</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Sharing his perspective on the new role, Jain said his journey at the company has been professionally and personally transformational.“What makes it special is not just the scale we’ve built, but the impact we’ve been able to create—touching over one crore lives across the country. As we move India from illness care to proactive, preventive healthcare, the opportunity ahead is immense,” he said.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On 